@startuml
title Ott-Based System Mini Reel State Machine

state Unregistered
state CreatingAccount
state AccountCreated
state LoggedIn <<choice>>
state WatchingVideo
state UploadingVideo
state ViewingLikes
state Discussing

Unregistered --> CreatingAccount : Create Account
CreatingAccount --> AccountCreated : Account Created
AccountCreated --> LoggedIn : Login

LoggedIn --> WatchingVideo : Watch Video
LoggedIn --> UploadingVideo : Upload Video
LoggedIn --> ViewingLikes : View Likes
LoggedIn --> Discussing : Enter Discussion

WatchingVideo --> ViewingLikes : Save
@enduml
